entry.value: ${filename:startsWith('diksha_data_summary'):ifElse("truncate table diksha_refresh;insert into diksha_refresh(content_view_date)(SELECT distinct content_view_date from diksha_content_temp) union (select distinct from_date from diksha_api_meta where dataset='summary-rollup' and cqube_process_status<>'SUCCESS' and requested_on >= (select max(requested_on) from diksha_api_meta where dataset='summary-rollup' and cqube_process_status='SUCCESS' )) union (select distinct to_date from diksha_api_meta where dataset='summary-rollup' and cqube_process_status<>'SUCCESS' and requested_on >= (select max(requested_on) from diksha_api_meta where dataset='summary-rollup' and cqube_process_status='SUCCESS' ));truncate table diksha_content_temp;", ${filename:startsWith('diksha_tpd'):and(${filename:startsWith('diksha_tpd_mapping'):not()}):ifElse("truncate table diksha_tpd_content_temp;",'None')})}
